text: Kevin Hughes may refer to: * Kevin Hughes (American football) (born 1988), American football player * Kevin Hughes (Australian footballer) (born 1963), Australian football player * Kevin Hughes (cricketer) (born 1966), former English cricketer * Kevin Hughes (Gaelic footballer), All-Ireland-winning Tyrone Gaelic footballer * Kevin Hughes (Internet pioneer), American World Wide Web pioneer * Kevin Hughes (pole vaulter) (born 1973), British Olympic athlete * Kevin Hughes (politician) (1952–2006), British Labour politician
